Example data.frame with KNMI downloaded data

A dataset containing the rainfall from January 1st till February 1st for Vlissingen and Westdorpe, as downloaded from KNMI

rain_knmi_2012

Format

A data frame with 1536 rows and 9 variables:

value

measured value

datetime

datetime of the measurement

unit

unit (mm)

variable_name

precipitation

longitude

coordinate

latitude

coordinate

location_name

station name

source_filename

filename from which the data was read

quality_code

Nan as KNMI does not provide this
